title: UFYB 53: Listener Q & A Vol. 5
itunes:title: Listener Q & A Vol. 5
description:
This week, we have another installment of the Listener Q & As. In this episode, we dive into topics such as dealing with overwhelm, empathy vs compassion, fortune-telling, teaching thought work to young kids, relationships, boundaries, and more!

 Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/53
